  <h2>Don't Let a House Slow Down Your Move</h2>
  <p>Relocating with a house still on the market is one of the most stressful financial situations there is — two mortgages, long-distance management, uncertainty about when it will sell. A cash sale eliminates all of that.</p>

  <div class="feature-grid">
    <div class="feature-box">
      <div class="icon">⚡</div>
