      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>Close on Your Schedule</h3>
        <p>Pick a closing date that works. We handle all paperwork through a local Wichita title company.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Ready to Move Forward?</h2>
  <p>Call or text <a href="tel:3163683344"><strong>(316) 368-3344</strong></a>. No pressure, no obligation — just a real conversation about your options.</p>

